article.description: — Eral Penn had 23 points as Long Island routed Army 90-65 on Sunday.
article.headline: Penn carries Long Island past Army 90-65
article.linkText: Penn carries Long Island past Army 90-65
article.story: NEW YORK -- — Eral Penn had 23 points as Long Island routed Army 90-65 on Sunday. Penn shot 4 for 6 from distance and the Sharks made a season-high 16 3-pointers. Ty Flowers had 17 points and nine rebounds for Long Island (3-7). Isaac Kante added 15 points and 11 rebounds. Tre Wood had 11 points and seven assists. Josh Caldwell had 11 points for the Black Knights (6-5). Kwabena Davis added 10 points. Jalen Rucker had six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
